➜美国热门专业风向标！这14类要被封锁的新技术可不得了！
http://www.sohu.com/a/285175698_101368	23233
<p class="ql-align-justify">日前，美国商务部工业安全局BIS出台了一份征询文件，将出口管制扩展到“新兴和基础技术”，意图在新兴和基础技术的出口、再出口或转让（国家）方面建立控制措施，包括临时控制措施。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181228/41af70a3d792481b90ba72e36f112d31.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">最新的管制包含了人工智能、生物技术、前沿计算等重点识别的新兴技术，看起来就像是全球未来产业方向，也将成为我们选专业的风向标！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">请同学们跟小航一起看一下包含的新兴技术类别吧！</p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>Biotechnology</strong></h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>生物技术</strong></h1>
<p>例：</p>
<p>纳米生物、合成生物学、基因工程、神经科学</p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>Artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning technology</strong></h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>人工智能与机器学习</strong></h1>
<p>例：</p>
<p>神经网络与深度学习、进化和遗传计算、强化学习、计算机视觉、专家系统</p>
<p>语音、音频处理、自然语言处理、规划、音频和视频处理技术、人工智能云技术、人工智能芯片组</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181228/a6ee2fcfa0274871b1eb83dc78be8b59.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>Position, Navigation, and Timing (PNT) technology</strong></h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>定位、导航、定时</strong></h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>Microprocessor technology</strong></h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>微处理器技术</strong></h1>
<p class="ql-align-justify">例：</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">片上系统、片上堆栈存储器</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181228/589a59e8ea4a4c21a9032e33e04e64fd.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Advanced computing technology</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>前沿计算</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">例：</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">内存中心逻辑</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181228/ff30f2daaf5a4fa0acb687ac134b09d5.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Data analytics technology</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>数据分析技术</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">例：</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">可视化、自动分析算法、上下文感知计算</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181228/507441dc1b2f4bfa8f4fcde2528e2ac6.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Quantum information and sensing technology</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>量子信息和传感技术</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">例：</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">量子计算、量子加密、量子传感</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181228/a8ebfdf25ce6437faff0bb4aa61fd372.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Logistics technology</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>物流技术</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">例：</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">移动电力、建模与仿真、全资产可见性、物流配送系统</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181228/8ab4eb8b66b04dd6951f62f8579b3fb4.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Additive manufacturing</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>增材制造</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">例：</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">3D 打印技术</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Robotics机器人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">例：</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">微型无人机和微型机器人系统、集群技术、自动装配机器人、分子机器人、机器人编制系统、智能微尘</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181228/b2c9e7e4a3a748d9b419d40adedc2f7d.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Brain-computer interfaces</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>脑机接口</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">例：</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">神经控制接口、意识-机器接口、直接神经接口、脑-机接口</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181228/e3233033c5474ec4baef888aeccdcebd.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Hypersonics</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>高超音速空气动力学</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">例：</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">飞行控制算法、推进技术、热防护系统、专用材料</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181228/972dbd8b85fb4efeac29df0e214d7133.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Advanced Materials</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>先进材料</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">例：</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">自适应伪装、功能性纺织品、生物材料</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181228/94405188afe6438dad294f82892d812f.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Advanced surveillance technologies</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>先进监控技术</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">例：</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">面纹和声纹技术</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181228/18b21a438a0043fdadafa9dc5e94468f.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这些都是最新最前沿的行业，也是未来最有用的精尖技术，从另外一个角度，给同学们做个选专业参考。</p>
